   <S PAR='131' RSNT='1' SNO='131'>In this faith of the truth we are being saved.</S>
   <S PAR='132' RSNT='1' SNO='132'>Our daily salvation is in this faith, in this reaction, to the scenery of the truth.</S>
   <S PAR='133' RSNT='1' SNO='133'>We all are short of the vision that comes from the faith of the truth.</S>
