   <S PAR='143' RSNT='1' SNO='143'>Did you bring them to the best scenery in My divine revelation of the sixty-six books of the Bible?</S>
   <S PAR='144' RSNT='1' SNO='144'>If the Lord would check with us in such a way what would we say?</S>
   <S PAR='145' RSNT='1' SNO='145'>God s eternal selection is toward this goal of complete salvation.</S>
